{"tid":2022062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾聲援反送中 報道疫情記者被捕","createTime":"2020-05-18T05:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T06:14:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea9d5e08e03d03479cf9dd95d1f1e2346c0c2c0","tid":2022062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200518/UE3MA72LK4AI37BTXJ45ZPIGAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200518%2FUE3MA72LK4AI37BTXJ45ZPIGAY%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCoWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=d1831a77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200518%2FUE3MA72LK4AI37BTXJ45ZPIGAY%2F&h=1822e18b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200518/UE3MA72LK4AI37BTXJ45ZPIGAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾聲援反送中 報道疫情記者被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200518/large/1589732253_d460.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200518%2Flarge%2F1589732253_d460.gif&h=bf48b707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公民記者張展被以尋釁滋事罪拘留。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n自2月起獨闖武漢記錄疫情的上海前律師、公民記者張展，上周五（15日）遭上海公安跨省執法從武漢帶回上海後，被當局以「涉嫌尋釁滋事」正式逮捕，是繼陳秋實、方濱、李澤華後，又一位因報道武漢疫情被拘捕的公民記者。曾任律師的她，去年9月因在上海鬧市撐着寫有「結束社會主義，共產黨下台」字樣的雨傘遊行，聲援香港反送中運動，被當局拘留兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，張展2月初到武漢記錄疫情，並在Twitter、YouTube等社交。。。。。。。。。。。式實施疫情管控，稱「政府以治療為名，將個體與外界社會的訊息隔絕」，「以穩定的名義，把疾病、死亡的人數掩蓋」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上直播武漢實況維權<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：粵恢復省內遊 首批逾120人<br />\n<br />\n上周三（13日）晚她還在漢口火車站廣場進行YouTube直播，。。。。。。。。。海的父母家，並把她在武漢的行李都送回去。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/網權網"},{"pid":"ee7d54942a61795ee62f3ba150ee5d96d341d0e6","tid":2022062,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Task1 Task2 Like retweet reply</span><br />\nTwitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家